More Bezier curves! Animated, this time.

Mike Acton himself responded to my last practice:

"@GrooveStomp For a follow-up from today, it might be a useful exercise to duplicate this visualization. https://t.co/esnSTxxPbI"
https://twitter.com/mike_acton/status/674774147017277440

Done and done!
I haven't done curve visualization since university, and it's really great to be retreading this ground.

Requirements:

- Pico 8: http://www.lexaloffle.com/pico-8.php

Setup:

Simply put `animated_bezier.p8.png' into the cart directory for your system:

Windows: C:/Users/Yourname/AppData/Roaming/pico-8/carts
OSX: /Users/Yourname/Library/Application Support/pico-8/carts
Linux: ~/.lexaloffle/pico-8/carts

See: http://www.lexaloffle.com/pico-8.php?page=manual